query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS archvizCompartments (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  constructionId INT NOT NULL,
  parentId INT,
  name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  description TEXT,
  `order` INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX constructionId_idx (constructionId),
  INDEX parentId_idx (parentId)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS archvizRenders (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  compartmentId INT NOT NULL,
  constructionId INT NOT NULL,
  version INT NOT NULL,
  name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  description TEXT,
  fileUrl TEXT NOT NULL,
  fileKey TEXT NOT NULL,
  thumbnailUrl TEXT,
  mimeType VARCHAR(100),
  fileSize INT,
  isFavorite BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE NOT NULL,
  uploadedById INT NOT NULL,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX compartmentId_idx (compartmentId),
  INDEX constructionId_idx (constructionId),
  INDEX uploadedById_idx (uploadedById)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS archvizComments (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  renderId INT NOT NULL,
  userId INT NOT NULL,
  content TEXT NOT NULL,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX renderId_idx (renderId),
  INDEX userId_idx (userId)
);
